name: The House of the Rising Sun

comments: Schwartz said the song was "sung by the band because it is meant to accompany action (the goodbyes) that is better performed if the cast is not singing while it is occurring. Of course, if the band is unable to sing the song, one has no choice, but ideally, it's better if the song can serve as sort of movie-like scoring to the action."
